  _playerName: Another essay? Didn't we write one yesterday?
  _NPCName: LYBL
  _dialogueType: 0
  _startDialogue: 0
  linear:
    _pharases: []
    _responses: []
    _haveResponses: 0
  branching:
  - _Question:
    - It's for my Latin Language class.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Oh I know Latin! Let me write this!
    nextStepIndices: 01000000
  - _Question:
    - Actually, I think I should write it.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Please?
    nextStepIndices: 02000000
  - _Question:
    - It's worth 30% of my grade, and it won't take that long.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Pretty please?
    nextStepIndices: 03000000
  - _Question:
    - You can write one if you want, but don't submit it!
    _NpcResponses:
    - Yippee! I won't let you down!
    nextStepIndices: 04000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - This looks good right? I can go submit it?
    nextStepIndices: 05000000
  - _Question:
    - Actually, this looks pretty good.
    - No, I can see several issues.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Woo!
    - W-what kind of issues?
    nextStepIndices: 0600000010000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Alright, I've gone ahead and submitted it, so now we can-
    nextStepIndices: 07000000
  - _Question:
    - What? I told you not to.
    _NpcResponses:
    - ... oh right. But it's fine right? You said it looked good.
    nextStepIndices: 08000000
  - _Question:
    - I did, but... why is it 111 pages long?
    _NpcResponses:
    - Because that's the minimum page count!
    nextStepIndices: 09000000
  - _Question:
    - In Arabic or Roman numerals?
    _NpcResponses:
    - What are Roman numerals?
    nextStepIndices: 0a000000
  - _Question:
    - You don't know what Roman numerals are?
    _NpcResponses:
    - No, there's nothing about them in my database...
    nextStepIndices: 0b000000
  - _Question:
    - Okay, what did the submission page say exactly?
    _NpcResponses:
    - '"Minimum length: III pages"'
    nextStepIndices: 0c000000
  - _Question:
    - Okay, it's only 3 pages. I can rewrite what you wrote, and then resubmit it.
    _NpcResponses:
    - It also says that you only get one attempt.
    nextStepIndices: 0d000000
  - _Question:
    - Oh.
    _NpcResponses:
    - I'm sure it's fine though! You just... put in extra effort!
    nextStepIndices: 0e000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - But uh, since it's been submitted, we can cross it off the list!
    nextStepIndices: 0f000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - Anything else that I can help with?
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff
  - _Question:
    - First, I said not to submit it.
    _NpcResponses:
    - ...
    nextStepIndices: 11000000
  - _Question:
    - Second, it's all Lorem Ipsum.
    _NpcResponses:
    - ...
    nextStepIndices: 12000000
  - _Question:
    - Third, it's 111 pages long!
    _NpcResponses:
    - Was that not the requirement?
    nextStepIndices: 13000000
  - _Question:
    - Uh, no? Where did you even get that from?
    _NpcResponses:
    - 'The submission page! It says "Minimum length: III pages"!'
    nextStepIndices: 14000000
  - _Question:
    - I think you mean "iii". It's 3 in roman numerals.
    _NpcResponses:
    - Ohh that makes more sense. But aside from that it looks good?
    nextStepIndices: 15000000
  - _Question:
    - Well no, it's still just Lorem Ipsum.
    _NpcResponses:
    - It's Latin!
    nextStepIndices: 16000000
  - _Question:
    - It's gibberish.
    _NpcResponses:
    - It's Latin gibberish!
    nextStepIndices: 17000000
  - _Question:
    - Well the good news is that you didn't submit this.
    _NpcResponses:
    - About that...
    nextStepIndices: 18000000
  - _Question:
    - I thought I told you not to.
    _NpcResponses:
    - I was so sure that my work was good...
    nextStepIndices: 19000000
  - _Question:
    - Whatever, I'll just write it and do a new submission.
    _NpcResponses:
    - About that... we only had the one attempt.
    nextStepIndices: 1a000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - I'll... I'll do better on the next task, though!
    nextStepIndices: 1b000000
  - _Question:
    - (Click to continue)
    _NpcResponses:
    - There is more for me to help with right?
    nextStepIndices: ffffffff
